{"tid":1469011,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔需要割𥱊 因為攪事嘅都唔係自己人 係喬裝嘅警察","createTime":"2019-08-14T00:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:11:33.000Z","uid":176026,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"374ad086e4c75e342eec206304cb7466a81be4e7","tid":1469011,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實連我地自己都分唔到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做咩要將個責任攬上身</span></strong><br />\n人地都承認曬有喬裝混入<br />\n我地機場一直和平集會無問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">係佢地一用喬裝手段就出事<br />\n好明顯攪事嘅係咩人</span><br />\n唔好再攬上身啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好再嘗試幫機場事件洗白<br />\n因為唔需要<br />\n都唔關我地事</span><br />\n<br />\n文宣要方向正確"},{"pid":"21418155fe9ccaf9e5298ab69a4cfc0336d72338","tid":1469011,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbb81a7327587868bc9dc80b8a6de3905833d2e5","tid":1469011,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:08:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c4b6fb1508ccaeb4155ba74f732e226f0cc1872","tid":1469011,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:11:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一撚早都係咁講</span><br />\n所有野入晒班仆街數就得<br />\n理撚佢係唔係<br />\n總之咁大發子彈唔撚係唔用下話？<br />\n齊上齊落就得架啦 無人俾人捉到就得啦<br />\n打人既 放火既 都係cosplay警就ok啦！<br />\n咁撚政治正確 食左屎呀？"}]}